<b>Yatappe</b>
<b>of Kibi</b>
Snake-Eyes Yatappe!

199
00:17:33.070 --> 00:17:33.120
<b>Yatappe, Kibi [BROKEN TYPESETTING!!!]</b>

200
00:17:33.120 --> 00:17:37.360
The bosses from each region
were here all along!

201
00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:40.910
To think I would see the day
where I serve you once more.

202
00:17:41.230 --> 00:17:44.250
I am delighted you are all safe and sound!

203
00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:46.960
Your compliments are wasted
on the likes of us.

204
00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:50.920
Indeed, as wasteful as
a bowel movement after a bath.

205
00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:52.510
Absolutely!

206
00:17:52.510 --> 00:17:54.680
That is for sure.

207
00:17:56.520 --> 00:18:00.390
They're so weird! And gramps,
you suddenly got all boss-like with them!

208
00:18:02.310 --> 00:18:04.020
"Gramps"?!

209
00:18:04.020 --> 00:18:05.300
Oh no!

210
00:18:07.690 --> 00:18:09.480
– Tear off his nails!
– Cut off his fingers!

211
00:18:09.480 --> 00:18:10.740
Rip off his ears!

212
00:18:11.620 --> 00:18:13.790
You better straighten up, you punk!

213
00:18:13.790 --> 00:18:15.990
Which one and how many?

214
00:18:15.990 --> 00:18:17.700
– Your orders, Boss?
– Your orders, Boss?

215
00:18:17.700 --> 00:18:21.860
That's enough! I owe him my life!

216
00:18:28.460 --> 00:18:34.840
We will lose no time in scraping together
any rebels that are still hiding across the country.

217
00:18:35.170 --> 00:18:37.180
Mm-hm! I am counting on you!

218
00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:37.760
– Understood!
– Understood!

219
00:18:38.490 --> 00:18:41.850
You escaped death, young man...

220
00:18:41.850 --> 00:18:44.510
Be careful hereafter.

221
00:18:44.510 --> 00:18:46.400
Like I care, you jerks!

