326
00:18:50.020 --> 00:18:50.060
<b>Flower Capital</b>

327
00:18:54.530 --> 00:18:55.820
What a surprise!

328
00:18:56.220 --> 00:19:01.040
So it seems, the man from Kuri
who made off with the blueprints...

329
00:19:01.040 --> 00:19:02.830
was you all along!

330
00:19:03.180 --> 00:19:07.330
We have been looking for these blueprints
of Kaido's mansion on Onigashima!

331
00:19:08.460 --> 00:19:12.090
Oh, but I put Sir Franosuke
through a lot of trouble...

332
00:19:12.840 --> 00:19:16.680
But now we can plan how
to invade the enemy's territory!

333
00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:20.280
You are quite amazing!

334
00:19:20.280 --> 00:19:22.970
Were you always so sensible?

335
00:19:22.970 --> 00:19:25.730
That's enough outta you, Dog!

336
00:19:31.810 --> 00:19:36.490
Is that you, Raizo? How are things?
Did you rescue Luffytaro?

337
00:19:37.150 --> 00:19:39.690
We accomplished that and so much more!

338
00:19:39.690 --> 00:19:43.540
It's a long story, but a rough estimate
of our current forces is...

339
00:19:49.500 --> 00:19:53.050
Th-Thirty-five hundred?!

340
00:19:53.050 --> 00:19:54.670
How'd we get so many?!

341
00:19:55.110 --> 00:20:00.910
Sir Luffy's safe rescued, and you
even found and freed Kawamatsu?!

342
00:20:00.910 --> 00:20:03.940
Oh, Kawamatsu had been caught as well?

343
00:20:03.940 --> 00:20:06.870
You took control of the mining camp too?!

344
00:20:07.440 --> 00:20:10.730
You accomplished far more
than rescuing Luffy!

345
00:20:11.850 --> 00:20:15.530
Here we come, Onigashima!

346
00:20:15.530 --> 00:20:17.480
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

347
00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:20.240
And there are yet warriors
who would join our ranks!

348
00:20:20.790 --> 00:20:24.700
However, I must inform you
of a lingering issue.

349
00:20:25.350 --> 00:20:28.620
Several weapons factories
are scattered throughout Wano,

350
00:20:29.030 --> 00:20:33.590
but almost all their products are
war machines meant for export!

351
00:20:33.590 --> 00:20:37.300
Samurai are more accustomed to
the use of swords and spears.

352
00:20:39.460 --> 00:20:45.430
Currently, procuring those is difficult
due to Orochi's ban on carrying weapons.

353
00:20:45.430 --> 00:20:50.850
If we cannot arm our rebel fighters,
the fight is over before it even begins!

354
00:20:51.330 --> 00:20:53.400
Right, that is understandable!

355
00:20:53.400 --> 00:20:55.620
The problem is serious indeed.

356
00:20:56.650 --> 00:20:58.070
Where can we find swords...?

357
00:21:02.860 --> 00:21:05.660
We have also made progress,
but I will fill you in later!

358
00:21:06.490 --> 00:21:08.780
I need to assess our combat readiness,

359
00:21:08.780 --> 00:21:13.960
so I'll head to Amigasa Village
and make it our base of operations.

360
00:21:13.960 --> 00:21:18.190
Raizo, tell me all about your group
when we meet again!

361
00:21:18.190 --> 00:21:19.610
Understood!

362
00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:28.200
Right, let's go!

363
00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:38.150
<b>Bandit's
 Bridge

Ringo</b>

364
00:21:34.600 --> 00:21:36.210
I cannot believe this...

365
00:21:36.900 --> 00:21:38.150
Is it really you?!

366
00:21:39.400 --> 00:21:40.240
Kawamatsu!

367
00:21:40.730 --> 00:21:41.800
Huh?

368
00:21:49.510 --> 00:21:50.250
It cannot be...!

369
00:21:51.180 --> 00:21:53.780
Wait... are you...?

370
00:21:58.380 --> 00:21:59.590
Kawamatsu!

371
00:22:19.230 --> 00:22:22.950
What a surprise to run into you out here!

372
00:22:23.860 --> 00:22:31.890
More than anything, I am overjoyed at
seeing you alive and well, Princess Hiyori!

373
00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:39.000
That's right, she mentioned that
a kappa raised her after her parents died.

374
00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:44.130
Please forgive me for running away
out of fear back then.

375
00:22:45.800 --> 00:22:50.290
Even if it was just a scrap,
you always gave me any food you found...

376
00:22:57.260 --> 00:23:00.400
Alas, my training is incomplete...

377
00:23:05.000 --> 00:23:06.320
Kawamatsu...

378
00:23:07.370 --> 00:23:11.360
I couldn't bear watching you
waste away, year after year.

379
00:23:11.360 --> 00:23:13.660
You would survive if you were on your own...

380
00:23:14.280 --> 00:23:18.290
I was plagued by the thought of my
presence causing your death...!

381
00:23:32.840 --> 00:23:34.160
Your Highness!

382
00:23:37.080 --> 00:23:38.520
Does this mean...?

383
00:23:41.180 --> 00:23:43.030
I'm sorry, Kawamatsu.

384
00:23:43.950 --> 00:23:46.860
Unless I act, you cannot survive!

385
00:23:50.170 --> 00:23:53.830
I was so afraid... I ran away.

386
00:23:56.990 --> 00:23:58.620
"Dear Kawamatsu,

387
00:23:58.620 --> 00:24:03.420
Thank you for everything.
I'll be okay now. Hiyori."

388
00:24:03.920 --> 00:24:04.800
What?!

389
00:24:04.800 --> 00:24:07.430
P-Princess Hiyori!

390
00:24:13.720 --> 00:24:16.230
Princess Hiyori!

391
00:24:17.030 --> 00:24:20.650
Your Highness!

392
00:24:29.400 --> 00:24:30.780
Your Highness...

393
00:24:32.240 --> 00:24:33.730
She is not here either...

394
00:24:41.710 --> 00:24:44.000
Princess Hiyori!

395
00:24:53.000 --> 00:24:55.310
Where are you, Princess Hiyori?!

396
00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:17.740
Princess Hiyori...

397
00:25:27.990 --> 00:25:29.550
Princess Hiyori...

398
00:25:31.260 --> 00:25:35.680
Your Highness... Where did you go...?

399
00:25:42.620 --> 00:25:44.610
Your Highness...

400
00:25:44.610 --> 00:25:48.430
Princess Hiyori!

401
00:25:53.620 --> 00:25:57.290
I am sorry. I am truly so sorry.

402
00:25:58.270 --> 00:26:03.330
What a kind-hearted reason!
So that's what happened!

403
00:26:03.330 --> 00:26:06.510
Thanks to you, I've plumped right up!

404
00:26:17.580 --> 00:26:18.350
Who...?!

405
00:26:22.390 --> 00:26:24.600
We've come to take our revenge, Gyukimaru!

406
00:26:24.600 --> 00:26:27.820
We're done with you stealing our weapons!

407
00:26:27.820 --> 00:26:29.860
Today, we take them all back!

408
00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:38.120
You gotta be unable to move now!
This magnum's for hunting savage beasts!

409
00:26:39.580 --> 00:26:41.620
Get behind the trees, Lady Hiyori!

410
00:26:41.620 --> 00:26:42.580
Okay!

411
00:26:43.830 --> 00:26:46.010
Hm? Are they with Gyukimaru?

412
00:26:46.010 --> 00:26:48.210
Whatever. Kill 'em all!

413
00:26:50.340 --> 00:26:51.880
Die!

414
00:27:00.230 --> 00:27:01.680
Kappa Style...

415
00:27:01.680 --> 00:27:02.650
Two-Sword Style...

416
00:27:02.650 --> 00:27:03.980
River of Retribution!

417
00:27:03.980 --> 00:27:05.100
Rhino Cycle!

418
00:27:17.910 --> 00:27:19.030
Master Kawamatsu!

419
00:27:22.130 --> 00:27:23.210
Kawamatsu!

420
00:27:23.210 --> 00:27:25.500
Are you okay, Princess Hiyori?

421
00:27:27.990 --> 00:27:30.170
Master Kawamatsu...

422
00:27:33.750 --> 00:27:36.740
Hey, wait! Are you running away again?!

423
00:27:37.260 --> 00:27:40.220
Bastard! Give me back my Shusui!

424
00:27:46.460 --> 00:27:51.440
Master Kawamatsu, I'm so glad...
to see you alive and well!
